<br>
I have no regrets staying evoc all the way to 60.  Evoc spells always seemed to be the way to go.  But now that we have a fire based conjuration nuke at 60 that is superior to our top bolt, I'm very satisfied with the conjuration arsenal.  The focus ring also makes the slower conj nukes more attractive.<br>
<br>
